加文斯基是開放Netscape瀏覽器原始碼的主要支持者，也是建立Mozilla專案的關鍵人物，但是當其他人決定重寫瀏覽器程式碼而不是逐步改進程式碼時，他對這個專案感到失望<ref>{{cite web
| url=http://www.openoffice.org/editorial/ec1May.html
| first=Louis
| last=Suárez-Potts
| date=2001-05-01
| title=Interview: Frank Hecker
| accessdate=2017-05-06
| archive-date=2017-07-26
| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170726130348/http://www.openoffice.org/editorial/ec1May.html
| dead-url=no
}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.wired.com/1998/07/mozilla-organizer/ | title=Mozilla.organizer | work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] magazine | first=Paul | last=Boutin | date=July 1998 | accessdate=2017-05-06 | archive-date=2018-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622192834/https://www.wired.com/1998/07/mozilla-organizer/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。當Netscape被[[AOL|AOL]]收購時，他撰寫了一篇文章解釋[[自由軟體|自由軟體]][[Mozilla_Application_Suite|Mozilla]]程式碼的性質<ref>{{cite web
| url = http://www-archive.mozilla.org/fear.html
| title = fear and loathing on the merger trail
| last = Zawinski
| first = Jamie
| date = 1998-11-23
| publisher = [[Mozilla|Mozilla]]
| accessdate = 2013-04-29
| archive-date = 2019-10-06
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191006162214/https://www-archive.mozilla.org/fear.html
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。他於1999年4月1日從[[Netscape|Netscape]]離職<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.jwz.org/gruntle/nomo.html |title = resignation and postmortem. |last = Zawinski |first = Jamie |date = 1999-03-31 |accessdate = 2013-03-29 |archive-date = 2020-11-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109023419/https://www.jwz.org/gruntle/nomo.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-54301216.html |title=Mozilla Founder Resigns on Open Source Project's Birthday. |publisher=Computergram International |first=Rachel |last=Chalmers |date=1999-04-06 |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523031125/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-54301216.html |archive-date=2013-05-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他目前在[[舊金山|舊金山]]經營他的[[夜總會|夜總會]]DNA Lounge。

